    clinicalSigns: ["Tachycardia (often >100 bpm)", "Fine resting tremor", "Warm, moist skin", "Thyroid enlargement (goiter) with bruit", "Lid lag and lid retraction (Graves)", "Exophthalmos/proptosis (Graves)", "Pretibial myxedema (Graves)", "Atrial fibrillation (especially elderly)"],
