    firstLineTreatment: 'Medical: Thionamides (Methimazole 10-30mg daily, or Propylthiouracil in first trimester pregnancy). Beta-blockers (Propranolol 40-160mg daily) for symptom control. Definitive: Radioactive iodine ablation (131-I) or Thyroidectomy. Treat the underlying cause (Graves vs nodular).',
