    patientEducation: ["Hyperthyroidism speeds up your body\'s metabolism - treatment normalizes it", "Anti-thyroid medications reduce hormone production - take as prescribed", "Monitor for signs of thyroid storm: fever, rapid heart rate, confusion", "Weight gain may occur as metabolism normalizes during treatment", "Discuss pregnancy plans early (need to optimize thyroid function)", "Regular blood tests are essential to monitor treatment response"],
